  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the effect of annular sizing strategy (MDCT versus
      TEE) in transcatheter aortic valve implantation on the prevalence and severity of
      paravalvular regurgitation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
